PrecisAuthority to enter into four SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENTS with (a) the Canadian National Railway Company and Canadian Pacific Limited, and each of the Provinces of (b) ALBERTA, (c) MANITOBA and (d) SASKATCHEWAN, which amend the Original Agreements pertaining to the transferring of title to abandoned railway rights-of-way to the extent of converting the particulars of the rights-of-way that were initially described in terms of railway mileage into ones that are legal descriptions.
